OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782043873
OL,3,CBurst water mains leave homes and
OL,4,Cbusinesses in Kent and Sussex with no
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FHomes and businesses in Kent and
OL,8,FSussex are without water or low
OL,9,Fpressure following two burst water
OL,10,Fmains.
OL,12,FSouth East Water confirmed that burst
OL,13,Fmains have occurred on Lade Wood Hill
OL,14,Fin Sittingbourne in Kent and
OL,15,FNorthlands Avenue in Haywards Heath in
OL,16,FWest Sussex.
OL,18,FPosting on its website, a spokesperson
OL,19,Ffor the firm said
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
