OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782043873
OL,3,CBurst water mains leave homes and
OL,4,Cbusinesses in Kent and Sussex with no
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,F"We're really sorry to those of you
OL,8,Fwho are experiencing low water
OL,9,Fpressure or no water at the moment.
OL,11,F"This has been caused by a burst main
OL,12,Fwhich we are trying to fix as quickly
OL,13,Fas we can.
OL,15,F"As soon as the repairs have been
OL,16,Fcompleted, your water will return to
OL,17,Fnormal."
OL,19,FIn Sittingbourne a road closure has
OL,20,Fbeen put in place so pipe repairs can
OL,21,Fbe undertaken.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
