OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782043873
OL,3,CBurst water mains leave homes and
OL,4,Cbusinesses in Kent and Sussex with no
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FThe spokesperson added: "We would like
OL,8,Fto apologise for any inconvenience
OL,9,Fthis may cause.
OL,11,F"We can't say just yet how long this
OL,12,Fwill take but please rest assured
OL,13,Fwe're doing everything we can to get
OL,14,Fyou back up and running as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,17,FMore follows.
